<h1>Which Venue &amp; Where? Details?</h1>

<p>Whenever possible, we will dance in the Palace. 
However, as an open-air venue, there will be times when the weather will not be suitable.
On these occasions we will use our alternative indoors venue, 
for the sake of the band as well as the dancers.
			<br>A decision is made as late as possible (up to 6.00pm). 
      If there is any doubt, the dancing will be inside, at 
			the Low Port Centre, Blackness Road opposite Tesco to the East side 
			of town.</p>
      
			<p>If the Scotch Hop is to be held in the Low Port Centre it will be posted 
      on twitter click here 
			<a href="http://twitter.com/#!/search/realtime/scotchhopp ">
			<img border="0" src="images/twitter.gif" width="40" height="40" alt="twitter logo">
      </a>
			</p>
			<p>you can follow us on twitter @scotchhopp</p>

			<p> <b>Google Map</b> locations 
      <p><strong> Need to tweak the main Linlithgow map so this one (for the 2 venues) also shows</strong></p>

